OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA cloudy start to the day but
OL,6,Fthe cloud dissipating by late morning
OL,7,Fwith plenty of prolonged sunny spells
OL,8,Fby the afternoon. Feeling very warm or
OL,9,Fhot in places. A brisk northeasterly
OL,10,Fwind, especially along coasts.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FA clear evening for most.
OL,13,FOvernight, low cloud spreads inland,
OL,14,Freaching many areas by dawn. Remaining
OL,15,Fbreezy, especially along the coast.
OL,16,FDry and a warm night in urban areas.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
