OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CWednesday:FPatchy cloud affecting many
OL,6,Fin the morning, clear for others. A
OL,7,Fbright and sunny afternoon to follow
OL,8,Ffor most. Breezy, especially at
OL,9,Fcoasts. A hot day, cooler by the sea.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,12,FPossible showers along the south coast
OL,13,FThursday, hazy sunshine elsewhere,
OL,14,Fremaining breezy by the sea. Sunny
OL,15,Fspells and mostly dry into the
OL,16,Fweekend, turning cooler but
OL,17,Ftemperatures staying above average.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
